#: blocks/gallery-overview/block.json
msgctxt "block title"
msgid "Agnosis Gallery Overview"
msgstr "Muhtasari wa Galari ya Agnosis"

#: blocks/gallery-overview/block.json
msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"Proportional, randomised artwork grid across all artists. Shows featured "
"artworks first, respects per-artist budget, supports medium filtering and "
"pagination."
msgstr ""
"Gridi ya sanaa inayolingana, iliyotawanyika kwa bahati nasibu kwa wasanii "
"wote. Inaonyesha kazi za sanaa zilizochaguliwa kwanza, inaheshimu bajeti ya "
"kila msanii, naunga mkono uondoaji wa vyombo vya habari na kurasa za mbele."

