#: blocks/submissions/block.json
msgctxt "block title"
msgid "My Submissions"
msgstr "Uwasilishaji wangu"

#: blocks/submissions/block.json
msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"Lists the logged-in artist's pending artwork submissions for review and "
"approval. Place this on your /my-submissions/ page or in a Site Editor "
"template."
msgstr ""
"Orodhesha uwasilishaji wa kazi za sanaa zinazokusubiri kwa ajili ya mapitio "
"na idhini ya msanii aliyeingia. Weka hii kwenye ukurasa wako wa /my-"
"submissions/ au kwenye kiolezo cha Mhariri wa Tovuti."

